snippet.title: Divine Sealing - All Bosses No Damage (Mega Drive, 1992)
snippet.description:
Divine Sealing gameplay.
Beating all bosses in Divine Sealing without taking damage.
Divine Sealing is an unlicensed vertical shoot em up game released for the Mega Drive/Genesis in 1992.
